Gay Judge’s Ruling Striking Down California Same-Sex Marriage Is Upheld

-- B y   K a r e n   G u l l o
-- 
2011-06-14T20:12:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-14/gay-judge-s-california-same-sex-marriage-ruling-upheld-after-claim-of-bias.html
A gay judge’s ruling last year
striking down  California ’s ban on same-sex marriage is still
valid even though he didn’t recuse himself before taking on the
case, a separate federal judge ruled.  To contact the reporter on this story:
